{"type": "article", "id": 44939, "title": "Nike 纽约用 AR 卖鞋，这儿有个丧尸主题广告牌 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-09-07T06:19:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 1928, "name": "AR"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170907124205alwTQibKMNp8uRO1.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的广告</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font: 18.0px Georgia; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><b><a href=\"http://mashable.com/2017/09/06/netflix-is-a-joke/#ttoOh9QMvmq4\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约和洛杉矶街头出现了广告牌，说 “Netflix 是个笑话（Netlifx is a joke）</a>”</b>。<a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/netflix-is-a-joke-billboards-revealed-as-inside-job-1035666\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">好莱坞记者</a>指出，整个事情似乎是 Netflix 主导的营销活动，以推广最新的喜剧系列。Netflix 过去一年的喜剧和脱口秀节目收视增长喜人。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.psfk.com/2017/09/pizza-hut-boxes-depict-stories-behind-delivery-orders.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>马来西亚的必胜客做了几款设计很精美的披萨包装盒，</b></a>有点酷炫。奥美马来西亚为其设计了这个营销，为的是让人们觉得在家点外卖披萨很酷。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709071325414h2TRa9sgztOY6oS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 22.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42054\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">刘力扬、满舒克为肯德基翻唱《我在人民广场吃炸鸡》。</a>不过在营销上素来活跃的肯德基这一波动作有点太慢啦。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z0024hcveh0&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42052\" rel=\"nofollow\">No7 化妆品广告，但是没露脸。</a></b>No7 英国 Boots 旗下销量第一的国民品牌（就是做了那个冰淇淋面膜爆款的牌子），广告由 2016 年英国奥运会击剑选手 Monica Aksamit 出演，把每次出剑和化妆关联起来。</p><p class=\"\">Boots 副总裁及全球产品总监 Kristof Neirynck 表示：这是第一次做化妆品广告没有展示明星脸。想传递出化妆不是给别人看的，而是为女性自己带来更多的自信和力量的概念。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=s0546130qpo&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/09/06/hondas-new-ad-shows-fits-big-space-inside-the-car/\" rel=\"nofollow\">本田旗下飞度汽车广告，拍着拍着把现场布景全部拆掉装进了车里。</a></b>以此体现车厢大容量的特点，类似的创意市面上也有过。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMzAwOTI2OTcyNA==\" frameborder=\"0\" 'allowfullscreen'=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/09/06/a-gruesome-living-billboard-swarmed-by-the-undead-popped-up-in-london-today/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国主题乐园 Thorpe Park 在伦敦郊外设置了一个丧尸主题的户外广告牌。</b></a>这个概念是创意公关代理公司 Taylor Herring 为其设计的。呃，直接看图吧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907133918NH9uMkcBzf6Gxrve.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709071339317Wc2xey3USAO5fC4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.thedrum.com/news/2017/09/06/ad-the-day-diesel-highlights-personal-flaws-first-campaign-publicis-italy-push-its\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>阳狮意大利给 Diesel 做的第一支广告</b></a>，拍摄了各种一字眉、斗鸡眼、平胸、矫正牙套……等等有“缺陷”的年轻人（模特）们，画面风格是复古胶片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907134215ugid5EnUHDFSNV7P.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561212\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>公司有什么事儿发生</h3><p><a href=\"https://news.nike.com/news/nike-makers-studio\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>耐克在纽约的 Nike By You Studio 设置了 Nike Makers’ Experience 服务</b></a>，通过投影、AR 等技术，让顾客在一个仪器上可以实时设计脚上的空白球鞋，然后在 90 分钟内做完鞋然后取货；该体验项目由 W+K The Lodge 部门设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907134453LQfASaP3Mv9YBg8T.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663394\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907134414oX1SYOBkbQ0mL6td.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663394\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：adweek</p>"}